WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.600 --> 00:00:05.570
The third stage is the review itself. The actual meeting takes place.

00:00:05.570 --> 00:00:10.070
In general, it should last no more than two hours, lest fasi fatigue set in and

00:00:10.070 --> 00:00:13.010
effectiveness, overall effectiveness be reduced.

00:00:13.010 --> 00:00:16.610
The rate of review at the meeting should be approximately the same,

00:00:16.610 --> 00:00:20.300
as that used for individual preparation. During the review meeting,

00:00:20.300 --> 00:00:25.430
the individually noticed defects should be collected. In most cases they should

00:00:25.430 --> 00:00:29.270
not be further discussed at the meeting. The detailed meeting process will be

00:00:29.270 --> 00:00:32.680
described after we discuss the roles of the participants.

